{"type":"message","id":"909bed93","parentId":"75e80d84","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:41:16.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我需要先检查 BAIDU_API_KEY 环境变量是否存在。可以运行一个简单的 Python 命令来测试。但首先，我需要询问用户大纲内容。不过，用户可能期望我直接开始生成。也许他之前已经提供了大纲，但在这个会话中没有显示。让我先尝试获取主题列表，这样我们可以选择一个主题，然后基于主题生成大纲。\n\n我需要调用 `ppt_theme_list.py`。但需要确保 Python 已安装。技能要求 `requires: { \"bins\": [\"python\"] }`，所以应该没问题。\n\n让我运行这个脚本。首先，我需要进入技能目录并设置环境变量。但 BAIDU_API_KEY 可能没有设置。让我先尝试运行，看看报错信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0a1e61303c164c83a18dd006","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ai-ppt-generate && python3 scripts/ppt_theme_list.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":256,"output":379,"cacheRead":17338,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17973,"cost":{"input":0.00002304,"output":0.00010991,"cacheRead":0.00078021,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009131600000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992473236}}
