{"type":"message","id":"f6492a20","parentId":"db5c8d64","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:41:18.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要设置 BAIDU_API_KEY。用户需要提供这个密钥。或者，我可以询问用户是否有 API 密钥。但用户可能不知道。我需要引导他获取百度 API 密钥。不过，也许有其他方式？让我查看一下脚本内容，看看是否有其他认证方式。先读取 ppt_theme_list.py。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_70d0738c26f5412d981f7e45","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ai-ppt-generate/scripts/ppt_theme_list.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":251,"output":184,"cacheRead":17593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18028,"cost":{"input":0.00002259,"output":0.00005336,"cacheRead":0.000791685,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000867635}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992476488}}
{"type":"message","id":"32919ccc","parentId":"f6492a20","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:41:18.250Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_70d0738c26f5412d981f7e45","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport json\n\n\ndef ppt_theme_list(api_key: str):\n    url = \"https://qianfan.baidubce.com/v2/tools/ai_ppt/get_ppt_theme\"\n    headers = {\n        \"Authorization\": \"Bearer %s\" % api_key,\n    }\n    response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)\n    response.raise_for_status()\n    result = response.json()\n    if \"errno\" in result and result[\"errno\"] != 0:\n        raise RuntimeError(result[\"errmsg\"])\n    return result[\"data\"][\"ppt_themes\"]\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    api_key = os.getenv(\"BAIDU_API_KEY\")\n    if not api_key:\n        print(\"Error: BAIDU_API_KEY  must be set in environment.\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    try:\n        results = ppt_theme_list(api_key)\n        print(json.dumps(results, indent=2))\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error: {str(e)}\")\n        sys.exit(1)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992478247}}
{"type":"message","id":"b58c31c2","parentId":"32919ccc","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:41:24.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所以需要百度的千帆 API 密钥。用户可能没有。我可以建议他去百度智能云申请 API 密钥。或者，我们可以使用另一个技能 ppt-generator，它不需要 API 密钥，但生成的是 HTML 演示文稿。用户选择了第一种，但可能没有意识到需要 API 导钥。\n\n我应该告诉用户需要配置 BAIDU_API_KEY，并指导他如何获取。或者，询问他是否有 API 导钥。另外，用户提到“基于上面的大纲”，可能他之前已经提供了大纲内容。让我询问一下。\n\n现在，我需要回复用户。我会说明需要 BAIDU_API_KEY，并询问他是否有。同时，也询问大纲内容。如果他没有 API 导钥，可以转向使用 ppt-generator 技能。\n\n让我组织一下回复。首先，确认他选择了第一种技能，然后说明需要配置 BAIDU_API_KEY，并询问他是否有。另外，询问大纲内容或主题。\n\n另外，我可以尝试搜索一下如何获取百度千帆 API 导钥。但可能不需要。直接告诉用户去百度智能云申请即可。\n\n现在，回复用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你选择了 **ai-ppt-generate（百度智能PPT生成）**，但需要先配置 `BAIDU_API_KEY`。\n\n## 🔑 配置 BAIDU_API_KEY\n1. 访问 [百度智能云控制台](https://console.bce.baidu.com/ai/)，创建应用获取 API Key 和 Secret Key。\n2. 在环境中设置：\n   ```bash\n   export BAIDU_API_KEY=\"你的API Key\"\n   ```\n   （如果是 OpenClaw 环境，可以在配置文件中设置）\n\n## 📋 大纲内容\n你提到“基于上面的大纲”，但我没有看到你提供的大纲内容。请提供：\n- **PPT 主题或标题**\n- **大纲内容**（章节、要点等）\n- **是否已有资源文件**（PDF、Word、图片等）？\n\n## 下一步\n1. 你先配置 BAIDU_API_KEY，然后告诉我配置好了。\n2. 提供大纲或主题，我将调用 API 生成 PPT。\n\n**如果没有 BAIDU_API_KEY**，你也可以选择 **ppt-generator（HTML演示稿）**，它不需要 API 密钥，生成乔布斯风格的竖屏 HTML 演示稿，直接打开即可播放。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":1497,"output":736,"cacheRead":16689,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18922,"cost":{"input":0.00013473,"output":0.00021344,"cacheRead":0.000751005,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001099175}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773992478251}}
