{"type":"message","id":"002d553e","parentId":"0bfa0c37","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:45:19.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这看起来像是一个OpenAI的agent接口定义。可能这个技能是通过OpenAI的agent系统来调用的。但OpenClaw可能有自己的agent机制。不过，用户只是要求生成PPT，我需要基于用户提供的讲稿来生成HTML演示稿。但用户还没有提供讲稿。我需要询问用户的内容。\n\n根据SKILL.md，第一步是“读取讲稿”。我需要用户提供讲稿。用户可能希望我根据某个大纲来生成，但他说“基于上面的大纲”，但之前并没有提供大纲。也许他指的是之前的消息中可能有大纲，但在这个会话中没有。我需要询问他。\n\n另外，我可以查看template.html，了解生成的HTML结构。但更重要的是，我需要生成内容。也许这个技能是通过一个脚本来运行的，但技能目录中没有明显的脚本文件。可能这个技能是通过OpenClaw的agent框架来调用的，而agent会使用LLM来生成内容。但作为助手，我需要直接生成PPT吗？还是说我应该调用某个工具？技能描述中说“将用户讲稿一键生成”，这可能意味着技能内部有逻辑来处理讲稿并生成HTML。\n\n但作为AI助手，我可以直接生成HTML演示稿，而不必调用技能。不过，用户明确要求使用这个技能。也许这个技能已经安装，我可以直接使用它。但如何使用呢？可能通过OpenClaw的命令或工具。但OpenClaw没有提供直接调用技能的工具。技能是通过agent框架激活的。但用户现在在跟我对话，我作为助手，可以生成PPT内容。\n\n也许最好的方式是：我直接根据用户提供的讲稿，按照技能描述的流程，生成提炼后的讲稿、幻灯片结构大纲和完整HTML代码。这样我就模拟了技能的功能。\n\n那么，我需要用户提供的讲稿。我来询问用户。同时，我可以展示一个示例，让用户了解格式。\n\n另外，我需要查看template.html的内容，以便生成正确的HTML。先读取template.html。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_34d6621c9b4344848fffd83c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ppt-generator/assets/template.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":109,"output":898,"cacheRead":20380,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21387,"cost":{"input":0.00000981,"output":0.00026042,"cacheRead":0.0009171,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00118733}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992713541}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ad0dc5a","parentId":"002d553e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:45:19.217Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_34d6621c9b4344848fffd83c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>演示文稿</title>\n  \n  <!-- TailwindCSS CDN -->\n  <script src=\"https://lf26-cdn-tos.bytecdntp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/tailwindcss/3.0.23/tailwind.min.js\"></script>\n  \n  <!-- 字体 -->\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.loli.net/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.loli.net/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  \n  <style>\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    \n    body {\n      font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', 'Inter', sans-serif;\n      background: #000;\n      color: #fff;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    \n    /* 幻灯片容器 */\n    .slides-container {\n      width: 100vw;\n      height: 100vh;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      background: #0a0a0a;\n    }\n    \n    /* 单个幻灯片 */\n    .slide {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 100%;\n      max-width: 450px;\n      max-height: 800px;\n      aspect-ratio: 9/16;\n      position: absolute;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      padding: 2rem;\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateX(100%);\n      transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n      overflow: hidden;\n      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #000000 100%);\n    }\n    \n    .slide.active {\n      opacity: 1;\n      transform: translateX(0);\n    }\n    \n    .slide.prev {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateX(-100%);\n    }\n    \n    /* 动态光斑 */\n    .light-spot {\n      position: absolute;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      filter: blur(100px);\n      opacity: 0.3;\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n    \n    .light-spot-1 {\n      width: 300px;\n      height: 300px;\n      background: #3b82f6;\n      top: -100px;\n      right: -100px;\n      animation: float1 20s ease-in-out infinite;\n    }\n    \n    .light-spot-2 {\n      width: 250px;\n      height: 250px;\n      background: #8b5cf6;\n      bottom: -80px;\n      left: -80px;\n      animation: float2 25s ease-in-out infinite;\n    }\n    \n    .light-spot-3 {\n      width: 200px;\n      height: 200px;\n      background: #06b6d4;\n      top: 50%;\n      left: 50%;\n      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n      animation: float3 18s ease-in-out infinite;\n    }\n    \n    @keyframes float1 {\n      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }\n      25% { transform: translate(-50px, 30px); }\n      50% { transform: translate(30px, 50px); }\n      75% { transform: translate(50px, -20px); }\n    }\n    \n    @keyframes float2 {\n      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }\n      33% { transform: translate(40px, -40px); }\n      66% { transform: translate(-30px, 30px); }\n    }\n    \n    @keyframes float3 {\n      0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }\n      50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.2); }\n    }\n    \n    /* 内容层 */\n    .slide-content {\n      position: relative;\n      z-index: 10;\n      text-align: center;\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n    \n    /* 进度条 */\n    .progress-bar {\n      position: fixed;\n      bottom: 20px;\n      left: 50%;\n      transform: translateX(-50%);\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 8px;\n      z-index: 100;\n    }\n    \n    .progress-dot {\n      width: 8px;\n      height: 8px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: all 0.3s;\n    }\n    \n    .progress-dot.active {\n      background: #fff;\n      transform: scale(1.3);\n    }\n    \n    .progress-dot:hover {\n      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);\n    }\n    \n    /* 页码 */\n    .page-number {\n      position: fixed;\n      bottom: 50px;\n      left: 50%;\n      transform: translateX(-50%);\n      font-size: 0.875rem;\n      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n      z-index: 100;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"slides-container\">\n    \n    <!-- 幻灯片 1: 封面页 -->\n    <div class=\"slide active\">\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-2\"></div>\n      <div class=\"slide-content\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight\">主标题</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-xl font-light text-gray-400\">副标题</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 幻灯片 2: 标题冲击页 -->\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-2\"></div>\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-3\"></div>\n      <div class=\"slide-content\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-4xl font-black leading-tight\">\n          冲击力标题<br>第二行\n        </h1>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 幻灯片 3: 金句强调页 -->\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-3\"></div>\n      <div class=\"slide-content\">\n        <span class=\"text-6xl text-gray-600 block mb-2\">\"</span>\n        <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6\">金句内容</p>\n        <span class=\"text-lg font-light text-gray-500\">— 来源</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- 幻灯片 4: 结尾行动页 -->\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-2\"></div>\n      <div class=\"light-spot light-spot-3\"></div>\n      <div class=\"slide-content\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-8\">总结金句</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-xl font-light text-gray-400\">行动号召</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- 进度条 -->\n  <div class=\"progress-bar\" id=\"progressBar\"></div>\n  \n  <!-- 页码 -->\n  <div class=\"page-number\" id=\"pageNumber\">1 / 4</div>\n  \n  <script>\n    const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');\n    const progressBar = document.getElementById('progressBar');\n    const pageNumber = document.getElementById('pageNumber');\n    let currentSlide = 0;\n    \n    // 初始化进度条\n    slides.forEach((_, index) => {\n      const dot = document.createElement('div');\n      dot.className = `progress-dot ${index === 0 ? 'active' : ''}`;\n      dot.addEventListener('click', () => goToSlide(index));\n      progressBar.appendChild(dot);\n    });\n    \n    function updateSlides() {\n      slides.forEach((slide, index) => {\n        slide.classList.remove('active', 'prev');\n        if (index === currentSlide) {\n          slide.classList.add('active');\n        } else if (index < currentSlide) {\n          slide.classList.add('prev');\n        }\n      });\n      \n      // 更新进度条\n      document.querySelectorAll('.progress-dot').forEach((dot, index) => {\n        dot.classList.toggle('active', index === currentSlide);\n      });\n      \n      // 更新页码\n      pageNumber.textContent = `${currentSlide + 1} / ${slides.length}`;\n    }\n    \n    function nextSlide() {\n      if (currentSlide < slides.length - 1) {\n        currentSlide++;\n        updateSlides();\n      }\n    }\n    \n    function prevSlide() {\n      if (currentSlide > 0) {\n        currentSlide--;\n        updateSlides();\n      }\n    }\n    \n    function goToSlide(index) {\n      currentSlide = index;\n      updateSlides();\n    }\n    \n    // 键盘控制\n    document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {\n      if (e.key === 'ArrowRight' || e.key === ' ') {\n        nextSlide();\n      } else if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') {\n        prevSlide();\n      }\n    });\n    \n    // 触摸滑动支持\n    let touchStartX = 0;\n    document.addEventListener('touchstart', (e) => {\n      touchStartX = e.touches[0].clientX;\n    });\n    \n    document.addEventListener('touchend', (e) => {\n      const touchEndX = e.changedTouches[0].clientX;\n      const diff = touchStartX - touchEndX;\n      if (Math.abs(diff) > 50) {\n        if (diff > 0) nextSlide();\n        else prevSlide();\n      }\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992719214}}
{"type":"message","id":"a602b01b","parentId":"3ad0dc5a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:45:21.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"模板已经包含了基本的HTML结构、CSS样式和JavaScript交互。现在我需要根据用户提供的讲稿来生成内容。但用户还没有提供讲稿。我需要询问用户。\n\n不过，用户可能期望我直接生成一个示例PPT，或者他可能有一个特定的主题。让我先询问他。\n\n另外，我可以查看slide-types.md来了解幻灯片类型，以便更好地生成内容。先读取一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e867c0e1bfff4878857358f6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ppt-generator/references/slide-types.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":3617,"output":217,"cacheRead":19750,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23584,"cost":{"input":0.00032553,"output":0.00006293,"cacheRead":0.00088875,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00127721}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773992719217}}
{"type":"message","id":"761bae5e","parentId":"a602b01b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:45:21.664Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e867c0e1bfff4878857358f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 幻灯片页面类型\n\n## 1. 封面页\n\n用于演示开场。\n\n**结构：**\n- 超大主标题（font-black，居中）\n- 副标语（font-light，灰色）\n- 系列标识/Logo（可选）\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide cover\">\n  <h1 class=\"text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6\">重新定义效率</h1>\n  <p class=\"text-xl font-light text-gray-400\">AI时代的工作方式</p>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 标题冲击页\n\n用于章节开始或重点强调。\n\n**结构：**\n- 单行/双行大标题\n- 几乎无正文（最多一行辅助文字）\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide impact\">\n  <h1 class=\"text-4xl font-black text-white text-center\">\n    不是更努力<br>而是更聪明\n  </h1>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. 金句强调页\n\n用于引用、名言、核心观点。\n\n**结构：**\n- 大引号装饰\n- 金句内容（font-bold）\n- 来源/出处（font-light，灰色）\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide quote\">\n  <span class=\"text-6xl text-gray-600\">\"</span>\n  <p class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white my-6\">\n    简单比复杂更难\n  </p>\n  <span class=\"text-lg font-light text-gray-500\">— Steve Jobs</span>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. 步骤说明页\n\n用于流程、方法、操作指南。\n\n**结构：**\n- 动词型大标题\n- 简洁说明（1-2行）\n- 可选：步骤编号\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide step\">\n  <span class=\"text-6xl font-black text-blue-500 mb-4\">01</span>\n  <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">明确目标</h2>\n  <p class=\"text-lg font-light text-gray-400\">\n    先问自己：这件事最重要的结果是什么？\n  </p>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. 对比页\n\n用于展示变化、差异、前后对比。\n\n**结构：**\n- 左右或上下分栏\n- 对比元素使用不同颜色标识\n- 简洁文字说明\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide compare\">\n  <div class=\"text-center mb-8\">\n    <span class=\"text-red-400 line-through text-xl\">传统方式</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-center\">\n    <span class=\"text-green-400 text-3xl font-bold\">全新体验</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. 数据展示页\n\n用于关键数字、统计、成果。\n\n**结构：**\n- 超大数字（font-black）\n- 单位/说明（font-light）\n- 简短解释\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide data\">\n  <span class=\"text-7xl font-black text-white\">10x</span>\n  <p class=\"text-xl font-light text-gray-400 mt-4\">效率提升</p>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. 列表页\n\n用于多点说明，但必须保持极简。\n\n**结构：**\n- 标题\n- 3-5 个要点（不能更多）\n- 每个要点 ≤10 字\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide list\">\n  <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8\">三个原则</h2>\n  <ul class=\"space-y-6 text-xl\">\n    <li class=\"text-gray-300\">• 少即是多</li>\n    <li class=\"text-gray-300\">• 专注核心</li>\n    <li class=\"text-gray-300\">• 持续迭代</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. 结尾行动页\n\n用于演示结束，呼吁行动。\n\n**结构：**\n- 总结金句\n- 行动号召（CTA）\n- 联系方式/二维码（可选）\n\n**示例：**\n```html\n<div class=\"slide ending\">\n  <h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8\">\n    现在就开始改变\n  </h1>\n  <p class=\"text-xl font-light text-gray-400\">\n    扫码获取更多信息\n  </p>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 页面选择指南\n\n| 内容类型 | 推荐页面类型 |\n|---------|-------------|\n| 演示开场 | 封面页 |\n| 章节分隔 | 标题冲击页 |\n| 核心观点 | 金句强调页 |\n| 操作步骤 | 步骤说明页 |\n| 前后对比 | 对比页 |\n| 关键数据 | 数据展示页 |\n| 多点说明 | 列表页（≤5点）|\n| 演示结束 | 结尾行动页 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773992721646}}
{"type":"message","id":"90a1d6c9","parentId":"761bae5e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:45:25.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我对幻灯片类型有了更好的了解。接下来，我需要询问用户提供讲稿。但用户可能希望我直接生成一个示例PPT。也许他有一个特定的主题。让我先询问他。\n\n另外，我需要考虑如何生成HTML。我可以根据模板，替换内容，生成新的HTML代码。但用户可能希望我直接提供完整的HTML文件内容。我可以这样做。\n\n但首先，我需要知道讲稿内容。让我询问用户。同时，我可以提供一个示例，让他了解格式。让我回复用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，选择 **ppt-generator** 技能，生成乔布斯风格的极简科技感 HTML 演示稿。\n\n## 📝 需要你提供讲稿内容\n\n请告诉我你的 **PPT 主题或讲稿内容**（可以是文字、大纲、要点等），我将按照以下流程生成：\n\n1. **提炼讲稿** → 精简、增强冲击力\n2. **生成乔布斯风标题** → ≤12字，对比式/问题式/断言式等  \n3. **设计幻灯片结构** → 参考幻灯片类型（封面页、标题冲击页、金句强调页等）\n4. **生成完整 HTML 代码** → 直接保存为 `.html` 文件即可运行\n\n## 示例格式\n\n你可以直接提供类似这样的内容：\n```\n主题：AI 时代的工作方式\n要点：\n- AI 不是替代人类，而是增强人类\n- 重新定义效率：更聪明地工作\n- 三个原则：少即是多、专注核心、持续迭代\n```\n\n或者更详细的讲稿。\n\n**请提供你的讲稿内容，我将立即生成 HTML 演示稿。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":4204,"output":478,"cacheRead":20488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25170,"cost":{"input":0.00037836,"output":0.00013862,"cacheRead":0.00092196,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00143894}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773992721665}}
